Package: animica-explorer
Version: 0.1.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Animica Labs <support@animica.dev>
Homepage: https://animica.dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
# If you build with debhelper, keep these substvars; otherwise you can remove them.
#Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.66), libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24), libgdk-pixbuf-2.0-0 (>= 2.42), libpango-1.0-0, libatk1.0-0, libx11-6, libxkbcommon0, libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0 (>= 2.40), libayatana-appindicator3-1, ca-certificates
Recommends: xdg-utils, desktop-file-utils
Provides: animica-explorer
Description: Animica Explorer desktop shell (Tauri)
 Lightweight desktop shell for the Animica blockchain explorer.
 .
 This package installs the native Tauri application, integrates it with the
 desktop (icon and launcher), and enables secure, sandboxed browsing of the
 Explorer with automatic OS keychain trust for TLS.
 .
 Notes:
  - Built against GTK3 and WebKitGTK 4.1.
  - Requires a recent glibc; see Depends for minimum versions.
